Automated Tests :


1) Create a new folder.
2) Put junit-4.12.jar and hamcrest-core-1.3.jar in this folder(Located in Test Files folder)
3) Copy the test code(Loscated in Test Files folder) with the other classes to be tested in this same folder.

TO COMPILE:

javac -cp .:junit-4.12.jar:hamcrest-core-1.3.jar *.java

or 

(For Windows)
javac -cp .;junit-4.12.jar;hamcrest-core-1.3.jar *.java


TO RUN:
Note: replace <test class> with the class to be tested

java -cp .:junit-4.12.jar:hamcrest-core-1.3.jar org.junit.runner.JUnitCore <test class>

or 

(For Windows)
java -cp .;junit-4.12.jar;hamcrest-core-1.3.jar org.junit.runner.JUnitCore <test class>



